    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利策略师威尔逊警告收益率飙升导致股市面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-warns-of-risk-to-stocks-as-yields-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利策略师表示，由于美国国债收益率飙升以及通胀担忧导致美元上涨，美国股市未来六个月可能面临艰难的时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-warns-of-risk-to-stocks-as-yields-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 10:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登禁止在美国大西洋和太平洋进行近海石油钻探</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/biden-bars-offshore-oil-drilling-in-us-atlantic-and-pacific</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登无限期阻止在美国沿海超过 6.25 亿英亩的水域进行海上石油和天然气开发，并警告说，在那里钻探根本“不值得冒险”并且“没有必要”满足国家的能源需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/biden-bars-offshore-oil-drilling-in-us-atlantic-and-pacific</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦政治经济学院特鲁博维茨：特朗普没有权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/london-school-of-economics-trubowitz-on-trump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦政治经济学院国际关系学教授兼菲兰美国中心主任彼得·特鲁博维茨表示，尽管唐纳德·特朗普在选举中取得了决定性的胜利，但他在获得众议院和参议院共和党人的支持方面仍处于危险之中。事实上，如果特朗普能在 4 月之前拿出新法案，那他就“幸运”了。彼得在“彭博社：开盘交易”节目中与 Lizzy Burden、Kriti Gupta 和 Guy Johnson 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-06/london-school-of-economics-trubowitz-on-trump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 09:43:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本烤箱制造商将以 16 亿美元收购富士通通用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/japanese-ovens-maker-to-buy-out-fujitsu-general-for-1-6-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家鲜为人知的日本烤箱和热水器制造商提出以高达 2570 亿日元（16 亿美元）的价格收购富士通将军有限公司，成为富士通有限公司空调部门的最新追求者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/japanese-ovens-maker-to-buy-out-fujitsu-general-for-1-6-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 09:18:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国债券收益率在 1190 亿美元债券发售前创下 14 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-30-year-bond-yield-hits-highest-since-2023-ahead-of-auctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格暴跌，30 年期债券收益率升至 2023 年底以来的最高水平，动荡的市场正准备本周发行 1190 亿美元的新政府债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-30-year-bond-yield-hits-highest-since-2023-ahead-of-auctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 08:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯计划进一步大举借贷以支付大型项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudi-arabia-plans-37-billion-borrowing-spree-to-pay-for-huge-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯是去年新兴市场最大的债券发行国之一，该国表示将在 2025 年保持类似的借贷速度，以资助大型石油多元化项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudi-arabia-plans-37-billion-borrowing-spree-to-pay-for-huge-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 08:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特上调二月份亚洲石油价格至高于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudis-raise-february-crude-prices-as-opec-holds-back-barrels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯将于下个月提高针对亚洲买家的石油价格，这一迹象表明，在 OPEC+ 近期推迟了增产计划后，这个全球最大的原油出口国在其最大市场中看到供应趋紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudis-raise-february-crude-prices-as-opec-holds-back-barrels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 06:08:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国宏桥发行2021年以来首笔长期美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-hongqiao-markets-first-long-term-dollar-bond-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着以美元发行的人民币债券需求不断增长，中国最大的民营铝生产商中国宏桥集团有限公司正在发行自 2021 年以来首笔三年期美元债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-hongqiao-markets-first-long-term-dollar-bond-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:31:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特上调原油价格后，油价持稳于 10 月高点附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东原油市场出现紧俏迹象，沙特阿拉伯上调了官方价格，油价稳定在近三个月来的最高水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 23:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
